snippet.title: Radiangames Fluid Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Fluid is the 4th game in the highly-rated Radiangames series for XBLIG.  

Race as fluidly as possible to collect all the dots and avoid the growing swarm of killer jellyfish. Use powerpills, vortices, speed pads, and teleporters to perfect your runs across 30 levels and 5 extreme levels.
